des:
A simple skill that tells hilarious jokes about various superheroes! Simply ask it to tell you a joke and it will pick a random one in our database of over 50!

Please Note: Superhero Jokes is in no way affiliated with The Walt Disney Company, Disney World, Disneyland, 20th Century Fox, Marvel, DC, or any of its subsidiaries.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
